headline: RTX to release fourth quarter earnings results on January 27, 2026
summary: RTX (NYSE: RTX) will issue its fourth quarter and full year 2025 earnings results on Tuesday, January 27, prior to the stock market opening. A conference call will take place at 8:30 a.m. ET to discuss the results and the Company's outlook for 2026.
